{"tid":285641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[口德]有人暈倒釀碰撞　6支那遊客莫斯科扶手梯滾落受傷","createTime":"2017-06-16T03:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T06:03:38.000Z","uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a239b257a1776a1abdaa75a35285c80a20b7bab9","tid":285641,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170616/s00004/1497581036359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170616%2Fs00004%2F1497581036359&d=e%2BxDHBxlilpaJVkZfg9g4P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0877e3a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170616%2Fs00004%2F1497581036359&h=1c5bb4c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170616/s00004/1497581036359</a><br />\n<br />\n<del>蘇聯</del>俄羅斯(唔知明報記者點解仲用蘇聯)莫斯科市中心一個地鐵站發生扶手電梯意外，7名中國遊客從電梯上跌下，當中兩人受到創傷性腦損傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據俄羅斯通迅社衛星網周四(15日)報道，事發於莫斯科市中心革命廣場地鐵站。目擊者稱，當時一群中國遊客正搭乘扶手電梯，當中一名女子感到不適並昏倒，撞倒其他遊客，結果導致7人從扶梯上跌落。<br />\n<br />\n工作人員隨即把傷者送到警察室，急救人員為他們急救。醫務人員證實，當中兩人受創傷性腦損傷，其他人則拉傷和擦傷，其中一人沒有受傷。"},{"pid":"b9464f6c05f4dca9c2ee2a7bc678e25f10e82a8b","tid":285641,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:04:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9e12c4806eda69aaa3a77807f36b9c9e395a73","tid":285641,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:30:31.000Z","msg":"蘇聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"2fd5825337e79b5a5dcee29a89297b664f41e8d5","tid":285641,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蘇聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\nForwarded to 新聞